des: As with previous years, My Wabash Valley Dot Com has created a partnership local golf courses to bring you this seasons Valley Golf Card. With each card purchase, you will be entitled to a single round of golf, 18 holes, at each of the participating golf courses on the card. Each of these golf courses is eager to have your business. Follow the offer to view each of the participating courses by visiting My Wabash Valley Dot Com.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
